
*** ROS package: amy_ros ***

amy_ros (ROS package) allows controlling a robot arm through the amy library.

To use/compile it, you need to:
- clone the amy.git repo.
- create a catkin workspace just here (in ws_amy).

To create the workspace (from terminal):
- move to ws_amy/src
- execute "catkin_init_workspace"

To compile the package (from terminal):
- move back to ws_amy
- execute "catkin_make"


> Nodes in amy_ros package:

amy_ros_arm




